laces individual pixel copying with a comple copy of the image buffer using numpy to shave time (possibly up to a few seconds) off the display update procedure. This was suggested here- https://github.com/pimoroni/inky-phat/issues/25\r\n\r\n*  BugFix: Yellow Inky pHAT now yellow instead of brown/black\r\n*  Enhancement: Performance tweak for set_image\r\n"}
